Package: scBatchCorr
Type: Package
Title: Batch Correction and Clustering Utilities for Single-Cell RNA-seq
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Robert", "Tonoian", email = "your@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    A set of reusable functions for batch correction, integration, UMAP embedding,
    clustering, resolution selection, and inspection of single-cell RNA-seq data
    using Seurat. Designed for modular, project-agnostic scRNA-seq workflows.
